# Hello Notion Vercel

- Deploy Next.js app (frontend) to Vercel; use Vercel MCP/CLI when available.
- Set env in Vercel: `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` for client; keep API keys and secrets server-only.
- Separate preview and production envs. Avoid committing secrets; use Vercel dashboard for sensitive vars.
